exceptions.tactic: apply (rel_curry_set_le_transport R sA sB a1 a2 a3).
exceptions.exn: In environment A1 : Type A2 : Type A3 : Type B1 : Type B2 : Type B3 : Type R : rel (A1 * A2 * A3) (B1 * B2 * B3) sA : A1 -> A2 -> A3 -> Prop sB : B1 -> B2 -> B3 -> Prop a1 : A1 a2 : A2 a3 : A3 The term "sA" has type "A1 -> A2 -> A3 -> Prop" while it is expected to have type "A1 * A2 -> A3 -> Prop" (cannot unify "(A1 * A2)%type" and "A1").

original: intros. apply (rel_curry_set_le_transport R sA sB a1 a2 a3).
